skdetail:

Invocation Name: hit trainer
des:
We’re proud to introduce this handy little skill that helps you keep track of your work and rest periods during HIIT workouts. Whether your into indoor cycling, running, lifting weights, exercise, workout, stretching, boxing, MMA or HIIT, this interval timer will prove to be an invaluable asset to you. 

This skill allows you to set the interval and rest periods and the number of reps you wish to do.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
